Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,# The Way She Flies 她的飞相
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,## 前奏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.28,0:00:02.02,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}来，我们学了什么\NNow, what have we learned
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.02,0:00:03.39,Flutter,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}很多的控制\NLots of control
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.39,0:00:03.85,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}很好\NGood
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:05.19,Flutter,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}大声尖叫\NScreaming and hollering
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.19,0:00:07.62,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}对，而最重要的是\NYes, and most importantly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.62,0:00:08.26,Flutter,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}热情\NPassion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.26,0:00:08.86,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}嘿\NRight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.99,0:00:11.56,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}那现在你知道欢呼的元素\NSo now that you know the elements of a good cheer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.23,0:00:14.53,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}来，听一个\Nlet's, hear one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.25,0:00:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}一...二...三...\N1... 2... 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,上！\NGO!
Comment: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,一道红色\NFlash of red
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼神的她飞上天\Nthe spectral wonder takes flight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.92,0:00:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,她很确定，她很坚定，她感觉很爽\Nand she's ready and she's steady and she's feelin' just right
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.38,0:00:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,她有热情，有动力，有决心要赢\NShe got the passion, the drive, the tenacity to win
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.99,0:00:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}而只要十秒她就能让你头昏眼花\Nand in 10 seconds flat she'll take your head for a spin
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,天如火烧，仿佛渐渐变成一颗密桃\NSky is burnin' and it's turnin' to a tangerine peach
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.80,0:00:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好像在海南岛沙滩的太阳下山\Nlike a sun slowly settin' over Huntington Beach
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.17,0:00:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,她的肚子里有颗火\NShe's got a fire in her belly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:00:55.80,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,嘿！\NYep!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:00:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛里有火\Nfire in her eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:00:57.17,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,对！\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.73,0:00:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,超音速的步伐在空中留下火迹\Nsupersonic strut leaves a fire in the skies
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,越发亮，变成温暖的金光\NBrighten up to a warm and golden glow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.61,0:01:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,让他充满你的从脚到头\Nlet it fill you all up from your head to your toe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.44,0:01:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,让那太阳闪在你头\Nlet that sun shine down on ya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.71,0:01:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都叫大声点\Neverypony scream louder
Comment: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,## 副歌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,七彩在天空中\N7 colors in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.95,0:01:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,看他飞过天空\NWatch her dash on by
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.62,0:01:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,天堂被遮住\NThe heavens are covered
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.26,0:01:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,被如此的景色\Nwith so many wonders
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.80,0:01:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱她的飞相\NI love the way she flies
Comment: 0,0:01:32.14,0:01:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,## 间奏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.14,0:01:35.38,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}吼，你要这样给我喊加油？\NUrgh, you're gonna cheer for me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.64,0:01:36.24,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}大声点\NLouder
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:36.78,Flutter,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}耶\NYay
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:37.38,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}大声点\NLouder
