Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:40.55,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}大声点！！！\NLOUDER!!!
Comment: 0,0:01:40.61,0:01:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.61,0:01:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有片青青草地\NWe got the green green grass
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.11,0:01:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,还有翡翠绿树\Nand the emerald trees
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.34,0:01:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,还有平原上的兔子、鸟儿，跟蜜蜂\Nand the meadows with the bunnies and the birds and the bees
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,而我，真希望能从她的角度看看\Nand I wish I could see it from her point of view
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.18,0:01:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,直接从那，一大片蓝天的中间\Nstraight up there in the middle of the big ol' blue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要是可以我一定还会带你去\Nand I would if I could and I would take you too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,飞过永恒森林，到坎特拉城去\Nover the Everfree Forest to a Canterlot view
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:01:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}飞到高空中，进入靛色的夜\NFlying high up in the sky into the indigo night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:02:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H60&}星星映照在你的紫色目珠，没有碍眼物\Nwith the stars in your violet eyes and no care in sight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有任何烦恼\NI ain't got no care in sight
